;Powered By Mozillians
Q'alajisan kuma aj Mozilla


;Mozillians are a diverse group of thinkers, builders, educators and hackers with a shared purpose to bring openness, freedom and participation to the Internet. Our collective global effort advanced Firefox OS from concept to phones in stores within two years, hosted 1,600 events in three months to teach the Web, and many more accomplishments. We’re celebrating our journey and the promising path ahead.
Ri aj Mozilla e jalajöj molaj chi ch'ob'onela', nuk'unela', tijonela' chuqa' majonela' ri kitzeqelb'en ri rayb'äl richin nikïl jun nïm runimil, jamalil chuqa' to'ïk pa K'amaya'l. Ronojel ri quchuq'a' xuq'i' chi, pa ka'i' juna' ri rutzij Firefox OS xtib'iyin k'a xtapon na pa taq royonib'al ri k'ayb'äl; chuqa' chi kikojol ri k'ïy taq q'i'oj, xunük' pa oxi' ik' 1600 taq moloj richin nuk'üt ri Ajk'amaya'l. Niqanimaq'ij ri qab'enam chuqa' ri xtiqab'än ri chwa'q kab'ij.


